《'''老大哥'''》是[[英國|英國]][[真人實境秀|真人實境秀]]節目。節目的參賽者須在一間獨立的房屋中居住數星期，並防止被公眾投票驅逐，最後勝出的參賽者會得到巨額獎金。節目名稱取自[[乔治·奥威尔|乔治·奥威尔]]小說《[[一九八四|一九八四]]》中的「老大哥」一詞。

節目於2000年7月18日啟播<ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/833942.stm | work=BBC News | title=Big Brother starts watching | date=14 July 2000 | accessdate=2013-05-11 | archive-date=2008-02-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080214175149/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/833942.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年9月10日前，節目於[[第四台_(英國)|英國第四台]]及[[E4|E4]]頻道播映<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11259639 | work=BBC News | title=Former air steward Brian Dowling wins last Big Brother | date=10 September 2010 | accessdate=2013-05-11 | archive-date=2020-11-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129060919/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11259639 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後因收視率下降，第四台停止製作本節目<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2009/aug/26/big-brother-dropped-channel-4 | location=London | work=The Guardian | first1=Mark | last1=Sweney | first2=Leigh | last2=Holmwood | title=Big Brother axed by Channel 4 | date=26 August 2009 | accessdate=2013-05-11 | archive-date=2010-09-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100914223219/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2009/aug/26/big-brother-dropped-channel-4 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，第五台於是決定製作本節目達兩年<ref name="channel5.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.channel5.com/articles/big-brother-comes-to-channel-5 |title=Big Brother comes to Channel 5 {{!}} Channel 5 |access-date=2013-05-11 |archive-date=2012-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406204503/http://www.channel5.com/articles/big-brother-comes-to-channel-5 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="express.co.uk">{{Cite web |url=http://www.express.co.uk/posts/view/238975/Big-Brother-is-back-better-bigger-and-sexier |title=Channel 5, Endemol confirm BB return |access-date=2013-05-11 |archive-date=2014-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103142021/http://www.express.co.uk/posts/view/238975/Big-Brother-is-back-better-bigger-and-sexier |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由2011年8月18日起與《名人老大哥》原版連播<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/mediamonkeyblog/2011/aug/03/big-brother-2011-launch-date | location=London | work=The Guardian | title=Big Brother 2011: launch date revealed | date=3 August 2011 | accessdate=2013-05-11 | archive-date=2012-08-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120829211803/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/mediamonkeyblog/2011/aug/03/big-brother-2011-launch-date | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

